<p begin="24690000t" end="39590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle0">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="40700000t" end="73690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle1">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="74740000t" end="142430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle2">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="260590000t" end="303930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle3">&#x202a;果實宣告了未知的將來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="304970000t" end="373350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle4">&#x202a;夢想蛻變成理想&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="415410000t" end="496760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle5">&#x202a;任誰都渴望落幕…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="517180000t" end="531510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle6">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="532530000t" end="565860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle7">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="566890000t" end="618880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle8">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="619950000t" end="668980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle9">&#x202a;總有一天我會讓你看到&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="670000000t" end="730980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle10">&#x202a;光輝閃耀的世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="807130000t" end="817020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle11">&#x202a;什麼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="818150000t" end="865820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle12">&#x202a;昨天又有23名&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;死於心臟麻痺的被害人?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="866860000t" end="897800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle13">&#x202a;我們才在懷疑KIRA是學生&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="898890000t" end="926870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle14">&#x202a;這些殺人案立刻否定這個論點&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="927920000t" end="957270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle15">&#x202a;這表示KIRA知道警方的情報嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="962290000t" end="987890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle16">&#x202a;如果L得知&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我握有搜查訊息&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="988980000t" end="1029250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle17">&#x202a;一定會想從警察內部&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;找出與我的聯繫&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1033360000t" end="1065330000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle18">&#x202a;一直有人在跟蹤你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1094420000t" end="1109090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle19">&#x202a;那還真是麻煩呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1110100000t" end="1132400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle20">&#x202a;我會盡快除掉他的,路克&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1146470000t" end="1160120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle21">&#x202a;因為死神的眼睛&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1161160000t" end="1197790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle22">&#x202a;一看到人類的臉&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;他的名字和壽命就會浮在眼前&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1198860000t" end="1279520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle23">&#x202a;死神可以把筆記本使用者的眼睛&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;換成死神的眼睛&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1284950000t" end="1312590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle24">&#x202a;死神眼睛的價格&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1313640000t" end="1353230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle25">&#x202a;是筆記本持有人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;剩餘壽命的一半&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1367690000t" end="1400680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle26">&#x202a;你怎麼做決定呢,月…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1401730000t" end="1431420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle27">&#x202a;第4話 跟蹤&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1439100000t" end="1464700000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle28">&#x202a;最近都沒見到路克啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1465790000t" end="1497420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle29">&#x202a;他把死亡筆記本遺落在人間界&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;是真的嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1498490000t" end="1526130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle30">&#x202a;可能被人類撿到了吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1527190000t" end="1544480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle31">&#x202a;不會吧?要是被人類撿到&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1545540000t" end="1572160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle32">&#x202a;除非持有人死亡&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;或是筆記本使用終了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1573230000t" end="1593820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle33">&#x202a;否則只能守著對方無法離開&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1594920000t" end="1634510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle34">&#x202a;是吧&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;但是路克不可能做這麼麻煩的事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1635630000t" end="1676240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle35">&#x202a;而且,聽說他有兩本死亡筆記本&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1677340000t" end="1705320000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle36">&#x202a;真的嗎?為什麼會有兩本&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1706370000t" end="1726960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle37">&#x202a;我搞不懂那傢伙的想法&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1748070000t" end="1802110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle38">&#x202a;若想得到死神的眼睛&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就得捐出剩餘壽命的一半&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1811470000t" end="1825120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle39">&#x202a;沒錯吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1826150000t" end="1862440000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle40">&#x202a;對,怎麼樣?要交換嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1877540000t" end="1886180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle41">&#x202a;路克&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1907570000t" end="1919170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle42">&#x202a;這筆交易…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1932260000t" end="1942150000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle43">&#x202a;不列入考慮&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2067730000t" end="2078990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle44">&#x202a;聽好了,路克&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2085410000t" end="2119770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle45">&#x202a;我要創造一個&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;沒有犯罪的理想新世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2120780000t" end="2155360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle46">&#x202a;並成為永久統治這個新世界的神&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2165490000t" end="2189490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle47">&#x202a;如果是延長壽命的話還能考慮&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2190520000t" end="2216800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle48">&#x202a;縮短壽命的話就一切免談&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2217880000t" end="2243480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle49">&#x202a;這一點路克也明白吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2244570000t" end="2293260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle50">&#x202a;嗯,我只是要告訴你&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;有這種交易的存在&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2294290000t" end="2335930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle51">&#x202a;如果不早一點說&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;以後被你埋怨就不好了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2345340000t" end="2371620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle52">&#x202a;「不早一點說」 ?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2372700000t" end="2392040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle53">&#x202a;現在才講其實已經太遲了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2393050000t" end="2416370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle54">&#x202a;這種事在見面時就該先提出來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2423750000t" end="2463680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle55">&#x202a;或是把它列在&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;筆記本的使用方法裡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2464790000t" end="2485380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle56">&#x202a;說…說的沒錯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2486480000t" end="2504450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle57">&#x202a;我好歹也是個死神&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2505500000t" end="2534850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle58">&#x202a;他卻不怕我,也不逢迎我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2535860000t" end="2566460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle59">&#x202a;遇到這類事情&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;還會一一挑出我的疏漏&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2619280000t" end="2627580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle60">&#x202a;然後呢?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2634960000t" end="2663970000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle61">&#x202a;沒有我必須要事先知道的事了吧?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2671660000t" end="2682920000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle62">&#x202a;死神路克&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2699020000t" end="2710960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle63">&#x202a;已經沒有了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2712040000t" end="2723980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle64">&#x202a;大概…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2725050000t" end="2745300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle65">&#x202a;是嗎?真可惜&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2746410000t" end="2758010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle66">&#x202a;可惜?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2759080000t" end="2778420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle67">&#x202a;如果不是眼睛,而是翅膀…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2779440000t" end="2806400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle68">&#x202a;我也許會認真考慮&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2807470000t" end="2845130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle69">&#x202a;「擁有翅膀,在天空自由飛翔」&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就像神一樣&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2852510000t" end="2888460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle70">&#x202a;這是人類自古以來&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;一直懷抱的夢想&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2897890000t" end="2926900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle71">&#x202a;長著翅膀在空中飛翔,這太顯眼了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2927920000t" end="2950900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle72">&#x202a;馬上就會被警察逮到吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2956950000t" end="2973560000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle73">&#x202a;我是開玩笑的,路克&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2986650000t" end="3027610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle74">&#x202a;但是像眼睛或翅膀交易之類的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3028690000t" end="3055990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle75">&#x202a;也許在不知不覺中&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;也能成為真正的死神&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3062720000t" end="3086040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle76">&#x202a;這樣也挺有趣的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3093420000t" end="3125050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle77">&#x202a;放心吧,月&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就算你不這麼做&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3126120000t" end="3164460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle78">&#x202a;也早就是一位很稱職的死神了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3178840000t" end="3211490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle79">&#x202a;因為現在的死神界正在墮落&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3212540000t" end="3240520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle80">&#x202a;淨是一些只為了繼續苟活&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3241570000t" end="3282180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle81">&#x202a;而奪取人類壽命&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;行屍走肉般的傢伙&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3288610000t" end="3338890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle82">&#x202a;沒有死神知道&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;自己存在的真正意義為何&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3340000000t" end="3370260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle83">&#x202a;或許存在本身&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就毫無意義可言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3393050000t" end="3438330000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle84">&#x202a;跟那些傢伙比起來&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;月,你更像死神&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3445100000t" end="3462730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle85">&#x202a;聽你這麼講&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3463790000t" end="3493140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle86">&#x202a;似乎我比較認真工作&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3503830000t" end="3522830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle87">&#x202a;但我可不想和死神相提並論&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3532190000t" end="3573830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle88">&#x202a;我身為人類&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;為了造福人間,才使用筆記本的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3596590000t" end="3619910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle89">&#x202a;不過,對人類來說&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3620950000t" end="3647230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle90">&#x202a;死神界絕不是無意義的存在&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3656310000t" end="3672920000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle91">&#x202a;怎麼說?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3674000000t" end="3687990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle92">&#x202a;難道不是嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3689010000t" end="3709600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle93">&#x202a;像路克你這樣的死神,1百年…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3710700000t" end="3740620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle94">&#x202a;不,即使千年才下來人間一次&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3741730000t" end="3763340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle95">&#x202a;也會讓人間界有劇烈的改變&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3771430000t" end="3806010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle96">&#x202a;死神界有著可怕的存在意義&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3807130000t" end="3820440000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle97">&#x202a;是…是嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3826820000t" end="3859810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle98">&#x202a;既然死神界已經如此墮落&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3860850000t" end="3873820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle99">&#x202a;等路克回去之後&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3874870000t" end="3892840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle100">&#x202a;不妨活用人間界的經驗&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3893890000t" end="3907540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle101">&#x202a;讓死神界煥然一新&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3920580000t" end="3976210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle102">&#x202a;月,你或許真的是個&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;思考極度正面的人類&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3994990000t" end="4010230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle103">&#x202a;那是理所當然的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4011340000t" end="4023280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle104">&#x202a;如果不積極正面&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4024350000t" end="4068380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle105">&#x202a;就不可能會想到&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;利用死亡筆記本來改善世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4103430000t" end="4112750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle106">&#x202a;原來如此&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4127120000t" end="4135760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle107">&#x202a;我明白了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4143470000t" end="4164060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle108">&#x202a;怎麼了?明白什麼?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4191520000t" end="4212110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle109">&#x202a;今天跟蹤我的那名男子&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4213200000t" end="4229810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle110">&#x202a;我知道如何得知他的名字了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4230890000t" end="4245560000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle111">&#x202a;你想怎麼做?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4246570000t" end="4275920000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle112">&#x202a;利用死亡筆記本的使用方法&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4276930000t" end="4304570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle113">&#x202a;寫完死因後有6分40秒的時間&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4305630000t" end="4336570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle114">&#x202a;可以記述更詳細的死亡過程&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4343000000t" end="4397610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle115">&#x202a;首先,我要測試&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;所謂「詳細的死亡過程」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4398720000t" end="4411340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle116">&#x202a;能控制到什麼程度&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4419740000t" end="4443740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle117">&#x202a;(隔天早上)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4475130000t" end="4483430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle118">&#x202a;是我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4499490000t" end="4522470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle119">&#x202a;受刑人又死了6名?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4533520000t" end="4557180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle120">&#x202a;心臟麻痺?是KIRA吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4570230000t" end="4578190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle121">&#x202a;什麼?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4584910000t" end="4613240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle122">&#x202a;有3人在死前做出異常的舉動?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4621610000t" end="4652890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle123">&#x202a;怎麼說?不是心臟麻痺而已嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4653980000t" end="4680600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle124">&#x202a;是的,死因是心臟麻痺沒錯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4681670000t" end="4705670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle125">&#x202a;有一個在死前劃破手指後&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4706700000t" end="4739690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle126">&#x202a;用血在牢房的牆上畫出奇怪的圖&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4740730000t" end="4779750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle127">&#x202a;另一個寫了一封&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;像是遺書的東西&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4780770000t" end="4825370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle128">&#x202a;第三個人還特意逃到&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;獄監用的廁所後死在那裡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4890210000t" end="4904540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle129">&#x202a;怎麼了,渡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4905560000t" end="4947540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle130">&#x202a;剛才出現了和以往稍有不同的&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;心臟麻痺死者&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4954610000t" end="4970530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle131">&#x202a;和以往不同?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4977300000t" end="5010630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle132">&#x202a;死者在現場留下了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;奇怪的圖畫或文章&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5011670000t" end="5019290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle133">&#x202a;傳給我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5046040000t" end="5065380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle134">&#x202a;畏懼KIRA的文章&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5079740000t" end="5112050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle135">&#x202a;雖說這也可能是&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;受刑人單純的個別行為&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5125780000t" end="5147390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle136">&#x202a;KIRA除了能操縱死亡時間之外&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5155150000t" end="5201450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle137">&#x202a;連死前的行為都能夠操縱的話…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5218540000t" end="5226500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle138">&#x202a;局長&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5243570000t" end="5266210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle139">&#x202a;關於這次的事件&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5267260000t" end="5309580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle140">&#x202a;對於新聞媒體&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;除了心臟麻痺,其餘不必多講&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5318980000t" end="5359590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle141">&#x202a;也許KIRA在進行某些試驗&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5360680000t" end="5370570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle142">&#x202a;若是如此&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5379700000t" end="5418040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle143">&#x202a;我們反而是在特地提供他答案了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5419080000t" end="5444680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle144">&#x202a;原來如此,我知道了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5451110000t" end="5486030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle145">&#x202a;用犯人做實驗…&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;真過分&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5487140000t" end="5519450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle146">&#x202a;簡直把人命當作玩物一樣&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5520510000t" end="5534500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle147">&#x202a;絕對饒不了他&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5555210000t" end="5582850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle148">&#x202a;如果KIRA是用犯人來做試驗&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5605600000t" end="5618220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle149">&#x202a;他的目的又是什麼?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5695020000t" end="5705260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle150">&#x202a;看吧,路克&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5713040000t" end="5766400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle151">&#x202a;爸爸的電腦裡已經輸入&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;那6個人的測試結果了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5767420000t" end="5787100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle152">&#x202a;結果正如我所料&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5788110000t" end="5810410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle153">&#x202a;死亡筆記本能派上用場了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5811470000t" end="5827390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle154">&#x202a;什麼意思&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5828480000t" end="5871140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle155">&#x202a;一位是照著筆記本所寫的&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;逃到廁所後死去&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5872190000t" end="5913830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle156">&#x202a;另一位在牆壁上畫了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;跟筆記本上相同的畫&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5914900000t" end="5960520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle157">&#x202a;還有一位寫下了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;與筆記本內容相同的文章&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5970630000t" end="6002940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle158">&#x202a;這三位的死,都如我所想的一樣&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6012330000t" end="6052600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle159">&#x202a;可是其他三人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我寫了非常理的情況&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6063390000t" end="6102410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle160">&#x202a;一位是一小時後&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;死在法國的艾菲爾鐵塔前&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6111770000t" end="6128720000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle161">&#x202a;在日本牢房裡的囚犯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6129790000t" end="6149470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle162">&#x202a;一小時後就身在法國&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6150470000t" end="6168100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle163">&#x202a;就物理學上是不可能的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6169160000t" end="6205110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle164">&#x202a;所以這個沒實現&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;只是心臟麻痺死了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6206200000t" end="6265250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle165">&#x202a;另一位我寫下了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;在牢房牆上畫出L的畫像&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6266260000t" end="6289580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle166">&#x202a;但不認識L的人是畫不出來的&#x202c;</p>
